lattice custom 1.0     a1 4.921 0.0 0.0  a2 -2.4605000000000001315 $(v_qb) 0.0  a3 0.0 0.0 ${qc}     basis 0.469700 0.000000 0.000000     basis 0.000000 0.469700 0.666667     basis 0.530300 0.530300 0.333333     basis 0.413500 0.266900 0.119100     basis 0.266900 0.413500 0.547567     basis 0.733100 0.146600 0.785767     basis 0.586500 0.853400 0.214233     basis 0.853400 0.586500 0.452433     basis 0.146600 0.733100 0.880900     origin 0.0 0.0 0.05
lattice custom 1.0     a1 4.921 0.0 0.0  a2 -2.4605000000000001315 4.261710993400000369 0.0  a3 0.0 0.0 ${qc}     basis 0.469700 0.000000 0.000000     basis 0.000000 0.469700 0.666667     basis 0.530300 0.530300 0.333333     basis 0.413500 0.266900 0.119100     basis 0.266900 0.413500 0.547567     basis 0.733100 0.146600 0.785767     basis 0.586500 0.853400 0.214233     basis 0.853400 0.586500 0.452433     basis 0.146600 0.733100 0.880900     origin 0.0 0.0 0.05
